-- China Needs Economic, Political Reforms, People's Daily Commentary Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-28T23:23:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/china-needs-economic-political-reforms-people-s-daily-commentary-says.html
China must deepen reform for further
development, a commentary published on the People’s Daily said
today. The commentary was attributed to Zheng Qingyuan, who
wasn’t identified.  The country’s reform and opening up faces a very
complicated and rare situation, the commentary said. The nation
has to “vigorously” push reform of economic mechanisms and
“proactively and stably” move on political system reform, the
commentary said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
